    <string name="connection_guide_content">
        <![CDATA[
        <b>How to Connect to PC</b><br/><br/>
        <b>1. On your PC</b><br/>
        • Start the Air Mouse server application.<br/>
        • Keep the server window open so it can accept connections.<br/>
        • Copy the local IP address shown by the server or encode it in the QR code.<br/><br/>
        <b>2. On your phone</b><br/>
        • Connect to the same Wi‑Fi network as the PC.<br/>
        • Enter the IP address manually or use the QR scanner to fill it automatically.<br/>
        • Tap <b>Start Air Mouse</b> after calibration is complete.<br/><br/>
        <b>Troubleshooting</b><br/>
        • Verify that firewall rules allow the server port used by the desktop app.<br/>
        • Make sure both devices are on the same subnet and that VPN is disabled while testing.<br/>
        • If the connection fails, re-check the IP address and restart the server once.
        ]]>
    </string>
