    <string name="sensor_info_content">
        <![CDATA[
        <b>Device Sensors Used</b><br/><br/>
        • <b>Gyroscope (3‑axis)</b>: Tracks angular velocity and powers the cursor movement and click gestures.<br/>
        • <b>Accelerometer (3‑axis)</b>: Detects linear motion, gravity direction, and scroll gestures.<br/>
        • <b>Magnetometer (3‑axis)</b>: Improves heading stability and reduces long-term drift when available.<br/><br/>
        <b>How the app uses them</b><br/>
        The app combines sensor streams with a Madgwick filter and gesture detectors so the cursor remains responsive while still filtering noise and tremor.<br/><br/>
        <b>Missing sensors?</b><br/>
        The app keeps working even if a sensor is not available, but some features will be simplified or disabled to preserve stability.
        ]]>
    </string>
